  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If you’re really good at what only you can do, it makes sense that you ought to charge more for your work.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If you charge three times the average, you can do 1/3 the work and earn 3 times as much.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Which means you can do less work for more money, and have more time to ensure that it’s beyond excellent. That it’s so good it speaks for itself.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "For the apiring artist, freelancer, or business, this is the goal. To be so good at what you do that people are willing to pay 3 times more to have you do it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Hence the need for a process:",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "listItem": "number",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What’s the average?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "listItem": "number",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What does 3x better look like?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "listItem": "number",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What do you need to do to consistently match it?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Figure that out and you’ll be one step away from charging what you’re worth.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
